{"tid":1023590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派完利市派大信封    傳支那滴滴裁2000人","createTime":"2019-02-16T01:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T08:53:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e35338ddee15f092bb612f654eb9f923cbb38b1d","tid":1023590,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20190216/s00004/1550254539816/派完利市派大信封-傳滴滴裁2000人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20190216%2Fs00004%2F1550254539816%2F%E6%B4%BE%E5%AE%8C%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%81-%E5%82%B3%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E8%A3%812000%E4%BA%BA&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=6869862b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20190216%2Fs00004%2F1550254539816%2F%E6%B4%BE%E5%AE%8C%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B4%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%81-%E5%82%B3%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E8%A3%812000%E4%BA%BA&h=f6df8506\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20190216/s00004/1550254539816/派完利市派大信封-傳滴滴裁2000人</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】農曆新年打工仔𢭃完「利市封」，諗住利利市市，點知跟手收埋「大信封」，就唔多happy。有內地媒體報道，滴滴出行創辦人、董事長兼CEO程維喺月度全員會上話，公司要做好「過冬」準備，今年會聚焦出行主業，所以將會對非主業進行「關停並轉」，裁減崗位重疊同績效不達標嘅員工，估計被炒嘅員工約2000人，佔比達15%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，滴滴又會開番2500個職位，但主要針對安全技術、產品和線下司機管理及國際化等重點領域，公司話預計今年年底員工總人數同舊年年底應該差不多，維持1.3萬人左右。<br />\n<br />\n稱開番2500個職位<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體「36氪」之前就爆出滴滴出行嘅內部財務數據，話其實公司舊年愈蝕愈勁，全年虧損擴大到109億元（人民幣‧下同），較2017年虧損約25億元大增超過3倍呀，單係司機補貼就用咗113億元。"},{"pid":"e3e9e13f73f088034425e4daa74956e3cee8baa3","tid":1023590,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828812fb6081c64bd4ac09dca6add949b91f77c6","tid":1023590,"uid":97451,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f743797d928ee64e2634ffd7e1a2fa5b2e17a1","tid":1023590,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"天滅支那狗<br />\n<br />\n13億支那狗死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fab762e73a9a00d8951db7934ec29bc56f34f9","tid":1023590,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"上市cap水 發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a43e82eb83a2fd4605542b4f9cca0b6c794843","tid":1023590,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:17:52.000Z","msg":"個2000人冇左份工唔洗擔心，你地仲有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9beeea0bbe773ecf273d6c50e32608199f3ffd5","tid":1023590,"uid":32114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"之前單身女仔搭，最後俾人姦殺<br />\n呢壇野抵滴滴執笠啦"},{"pid":"69283b909f108bfd087531aaa15a56f4f50ea946","tid":1023590,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9beeea0bbe773ecf273d6c50e32608199f3ffd5","tid":1023590,"uid":32114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"之前單身女仔搭，最後俾人姦殺<br />\n呢壇野抵滴滴執笠啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"搞到咁即刻冇人敢搭<br />\n支那畜生搞呢d服務真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"7ece389c78bd2e4a757984784d57fdcc39d3ee13","tid":1023590,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},{"pid":"cb20fdd1b5c8e0cf895da60728445592ab6640e0","tid":1023590,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0401d84797192fb4a68095161d5c5ac814cd9e","tid":1023590,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69283b909f108bfd087531aaa15a56f4f50ea946","tid":1023590,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"sc